686
00:30:26,880 --> 00:30:27,720
What do you want?

687
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:30,030
You sound energetic.

688
00:30:30,400 --> 00:30:31,510
That's a relief.

689
00:30:32,160 --> 00:30:34,160
I picked up fine herbs

690
00:30:34,400 --> 00:30:35,600
for you

691
00:30:35,600 --> 00:30:36,920
