703
00:31:02,960 --> 00:31:05,270
The honorable Lord Wei wouldn't...

704
00:31:08,270 --> 00:31:09,110
What's up?

705
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:10,230
What's on your mind?

706
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:13,760
Nothing.

707
00:31:14,360 --> 00:31:15,360
Cijiu,

708
00:31:15,360 --> 00:31:17,360
