719
00:31:39,710 --> 00:31:40,920
Give it a go.

720
00:31:41,300 --> 00:31:42,570
You won't know if you don't try.

721
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:43,520
Have a try.

722
00:31:43,710 --> 00:31:45,680
Try it, please!

723
00:31:46,120 --> 00:31:47,310
