724
00:31:47,400 --> 00:31:48,640
Yes, you do that.

725
00:31:48,640 --> 00:31:50,120
Relax. I'll massage you.

726
00:31:51,710 --> 00:31:52,750
Over here.

727
00:31:54,550 --> 00:31:55,510
Easy!

728
00:31:56,640 --> 00:31:57,480
So

729
00:31:57,490 --> 00:31:59,400
Lin'an is on her way back.

730
00:31:59,600 --> 00:32:00,440
Yes.

731
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:01,840
Hearing that Xu Qi'an died,

732
00:32:02,030 --> 00:32:04,230
she made sure Duchess Yu was fine

733
00:32:04,230 --> 00:32:05,840
and rode back immediately.

734
00:32:05,840 --> 00:32:06,680
However...

735
00:32:08,230 --> 00:32:09,070
What's wrong?

736
00:32:09,750 --> 00:32:11,680
Princess Lin'an took the wrong path

737
00:32:11,680 --> 00:32:12,600
in haste.

738
00:32:13,510 --> 00:32:14,790
She could've taken the main road

739
00:32:14,790 --> 00:32:16,160
and arrived in three days,

740
00:32:16,550 --> 00:32:17,940
but she strayed into the Dark Forest

741
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:19,270
to take a shortcut.

742
00:32:19,470 --> 00:32:21,550
Bandits were all over that place.

743
00:32:21,790 --> 00:32:22,960
To protect Her Highness,

744
00:32:23,030 --> 00:32:24,990
we contacted local authorities in secret

745
00:32:25,230 --> 00:32:26,510
and wiped out

746
00:32:26,510 --> 00:32:27,470
all those bandits.

747
00:32:29,600 --> 00:32:30,600
As soon as

748
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:32,270
she got out,

749
00:32:32,640 --> 00:32:34,160
she ended up in the Sand Col

750
00:32:34,270 --> 00:32:35,550
in the desert.

751
