753
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:40,280
We had to

754
00:32:40,360 --> 00:32:41,680
show up

755
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:43,160
as members of a trade caravan

756
00:32:43,160 --> 00:32:44,160
to save her life.

757
00:32:46,550 --> 00:32:48,030
You had us protect her covertly,

758
00:32:48,120 --> 00:32:49,470
