873
00:40:13,920 --> 00:40:14,760
Eat your melon.

874
00:40:15,320 --> 00:40:16,280
I am.

875
00:40:17,470 --> 00:40:18,310
Sir,

876
00:40:18,510 --> 00:40:19,350
two more, please.

877
00:40:28,700 --> 00:40:29,820
It's too hot, isn't it?

878
00:40:37,550 --> 00:40:38,800
Slow down. Don't choke on it.

879
00:40:39,550 --> 00:40:40,390
Give me two more.

880
00:40:54,070 --> 00:40:54,910
Cijiu,

881
00:40:55,400 --> 00:40:56,800
it's been another four hours.

882
00:40:57,030 --> 00:40:58,320
We can't keep waiting.

883
00:40:58,630 --> 00:41:00,670
Or my stomach will explode.

884
00:41:01,150 --> 00:41:03,070
I don't think your friend will come.

885
00:41:04,110 --> 00:41:05,880
I guess that person doesn't want to see me.

886
00:41:11,030 --> 00:41:12,360
Who exactly is it?

887
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:17,070
When I used to set off lanterns from home,

888
00:41:17,190 --> 00:41:18,550
my friend would come the next day.

889
00:41:18,920 --> 00:41:20,240
I never got stood up once.

890
00:41:21,030 --> 00:41:22,190
But now...

891
00:41:24,090 --> 00:41:25,750
"Two sticks of grass stay firmly together.

892
00:41:26,400 --> 00:41:27,240
Yet two hearts

893
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:29,240
can't be as firm."

894
00:41:31,070 --> 00:41:31,910
Indeed.

895
00:41:32,110 --> 00:41:34,920
Your friend stood you up
without prior notice.

896
00:41:34,920 --> 00:41:36,110
How mean.

897
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:39,720
Hold on.

898
00:41:40,630 --> 00:41:42,110
You set off lanterns from home.

899
00:41:42,550 --> 00:41:43,470
Which home?

900
00:41:48,240 --> 00:41:49,080
Right.

901
00:41:49,190 --> 00:41:50,150
We've moved.

902
00:41:53,400 --> 00:41:55,090
It's not that my friend refuses to see me.

903
00:41:55,320 --> 00:41:56,400
It's not, right?

904
00:41:56,840 --> 00:41:57,680
Come on.

905
00:41:58,880 --> 00:41:59,720
Let's go.

906
00:42:04,470 --> 00:42:06,110
It's a long trip, Your Highness.

907
00:42:06,110 --> 00:42:08,170
Going back alone is too dangerous.

908
00:42:08,170 --> 00:42:09,120
(Xu Residence)

909
00:42:09,120 --> 00:42:10,630
(Xu Qi'an died.)

910
00:42:10,630 --> 00:42:11,700
(He's dead!)

911
00:42:12,920 --> 00:42:15,720
(I have to see him one last time.)

912
00:42:16,440 --> 00:42:17,470
(Xu Qi'an,)

913
00:42:17,480 --> 00:42:18,320
(wait for me.)

914
00:42:18,880 --> 00:42:20,510
(That's an order!)

915
00:42:26,510 --> 00:42:27,350
Miss, are you

916
00:42:27,360 --> 00:42:28,200
