917
00:42:28,300 --> 00:42:29,900
The Xu Family moved away a long time ago.

918
00:42:40,500 --> 00:42:43,140
(Meixi Bridge)

919
00:42:45,240 --> 00:42:46,080
Cijiu,

920
00:42:46,510 --> 00:42:47,920
