921
00:42:48,240 --> 00:42:49,360
It's windy tonight.

922
00:42:49,670 --> 00:42:51,470
We'll succeed in this way.

923
00:42:56,030 --> 00:42:57,240
Hold the thread.

924
00:42:57,240 --> 00:42:58,840
Don't let it go. I'm almost done.

925
00:42:59,320 --> 00:43:01,470
Don't you trust your brother?

926
00:43:01,470 --> 00:43:02,960
I trust you the least.

927
00:43:02,960 --> 00:43:04,670
If so, ask your father to do this.

928
00:43:09,400 --> 00:43:10,360
Xu Qi'an...!

929
00:43:10,470 --> 00:43:13,610
♪Thankfully, you came as the autumn wind♪

930
00:43:13,610 --> 00:43:15,840
